Orion Capital Corp said it acquired163,000 shares of Twin Disc Inc common stock, or 5.2 pct of thecompany's common stock outstanding.    In a filing with the Securities and Exchange Commission,Orion Capital said the stock represents "a favorable investmentopportunity at current market prices."    In open market transactions between August 21 and October16, an Orion Capital subsidiary bought 56,200 Twin Disc commonshares at 21.06 dlrs to 22.43 dlrs a share. The entire 5.2 pctstake was purchased at a cost of 3.2 mln dlrs, Orion Capitaltold the SEC.     Reuter&#3;